== Our primary public mailing List ==

Kindly hosted by [https://lists.ourproject.org/mailman/listinfo Ourprojects.org] our current list was started in 2011. It replaced our older P2P Research list which was active since 2007.

It's a lively list, and you can expect at least 5-10 emails daily, and sometimes quite a bit more.

Please read our [[Recommended Guidelines and Good practises]] before subscribing. These guidelines apply across all P2P Foundations web forums.

* Subscribe to the list: http://lists.ourproject.org/cgi-bin/mailman/listinfo/p2p-foundation
* Read the archives of the list: https://lists.ourproject.org/pipermail/p2p-foundation/

=== We also host a number of private and public lists ===
As of 2014 we now have our own list serv for hosting lists for community projects [http://lists.p2pfoundation.net lists.p2pfoundation.net]

